room_title: Escape room "The Oracle's Alley" by Old Town Escape in Mankato
review: My wife and I stopped by last night as a surprise to her and we attempted the 2-3 person room. We both had a great time and are looking forward to attempting another one soon!

room_title: Escape room "The Oracle's Alley" by Old Town Escape in Mankato
review: Oracle's Alley was a great date night! Hubby and I had a blast and it was so fun to do something different like this. We had a great time working together to figure out the clues. Now we'll have to come back with friends to try the other rooms!
